#include<stdio.h>
main()
{
  int a[100][4],b[100][4],i,j,n;
  scanf("%d",&n);
  for(i=0;i<n;i++)
  {
     scanf("%d%d%d%d",&a[i][0],&a[i][1],&a[i][2],&a[i][3]);
     scanf("%d%d%d%d",&b[i][0],&b[i][1],&b[i][2],&b[i][3]);
  }
  for(i=0;i<n;i++)
  {
    if(a[i][2]>b[i][0]&&a[i][3]>b[i][1])
    {
       printf("%d %d %d %d\n",((a[i][0]>b[i][0])?a[i][0]:b[i][0]),((a[i][1]>b[i][1])?a[i][1]:b[i][1]),((a[i][2]>b[i][2])?b[i][2]:a[i][2]),((a[i][3]>b[i][3])?b[i][3]:a[i][3]));
    }
    else
      printf("No Overlap\n");
  }
  return 0;
}
